# Regenerable run artifacts. Stage 0 rebuilds data/; Stage 1-3 rebuild results/.
# results/figures/ is deliberately NOT ignored — curated figures are committed.
# Wildcard (not just "results/runs/") so ad hoc validation dirs like results/runs_v2/
# are covered too, without needing a .gitignore edit every time one is created.
